GULF OF MEXICO.
FLORIDA TO TEXAS.
50 FOOT S/V HOLE KAY, WHITE HULL, THREE PERSONS ON BOARD,
OVERDUE KEY WEST (24-33.5N 081-47.0W) TO
HOUSTON (29-45.8N 095-23.0W). VESSELS IN
VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO RCC MIAMI,
PHONE: 305 415 6800, E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
